                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18060219-57-defend596 t18060219-57-punish318"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>GALLOWAY - <rs id="t18060219-57-verdict319" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18060219-57-verdict319" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
